模块 com.example.bubblebobble
程序包 com.ae2dms.model.gameObject

类 GameObject

java.lang.Object
com.ae2dms.model.gameObject.GameObject
直接已知子类:
SpriteObject, WallObject
public abstract class GameObject extends Object
The type Game object defines common behavior and parameter among all the game objects. All the objects would have its x-coordinate, y-coordinate , width, height and image.
